{"tid":1084302,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone處理器開發主管驚傳離職　A7到A12X都他主導設計","createTime":"2019-03-30T09:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T02:12:44.000Z","uid":52127,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"eca11b1c8fff78147143ab7e2830585317f2170e","tid":1084302,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"美國蘋果公司（Apple）正擴大掌控自家晶片設計，如今卻傳出主導iPhone、iPad處理器<br />\n設計的首席架構師離職。 <br />\n美國科技媒體Cnet引述知情人士消息，領導蘋果從A7到A12X晶片設計的重要人物－－威廉<br />\n斯（Gerard Williams III）上個月已離職。 <br />\n威廉斯在外界知名度不高，卻是蘋果重量級的半導體工程師之1。他在蘋果工作9年，離職<br />\n前是平台架構的高級主管。 <br />\n威廉斯離職的原因不確定，目前也沒跳槽其它公司。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，從蘋果第1款64位元行動設備處理器A7，到最新iPad Pro所採用的A12X晶片，<br />\n每款處理器核心都是威廉斯主導開發。 <br />\n最近幾年，威廉斯職責除了設計蘋果晶片的CPU核心，也負責系統單晶片（SoC）各種部位<br />\n的配置。 <br />\nCnet報導說，威廉斯離職是蘋果損失，超過60項蘋果專利的發明人是他，包含電力管理、<br />\n記憶壓縮及多核處理器等，未來處理器仍可看出他的影響力。 <br />\n<br />\n蘋果一如以往，婉拒回應傳聞報導。<br />\n<br />\n為了區隔對手並擴大對設備的掌控，使蘋果決定自行研發晶片。蘋果自行開發iPhone、<br />\niPad處理晶片已多年，最近開始設計更多零組件，包括配對AirPods和手機的藍芽晶片，<br />\n以及儲存指紋和其它重要資訊的安全晶片。 <br />\n先前有報導說，蘋果也在開發圖像處理器、數據機和電源管理等晶片。（吳國仲╱綜合外<br />\n電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20190330/1542505/?itm_source=twad_web&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_campaign=twad_marquee&amp;itm_content=marquee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190330%2F1542505%2F%3Fitm_source%3Dtwad_web%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_campaign%3Dtwad_marquee%26itm_content%3Dmarquee&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6jcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=097ce578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.finance.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190330%2F1542505%2F%3Fitm_source%3Dtwad_web%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_campaign%3Dtwad_marquee%26itm_content%3Dmarquee&h=98cac6ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.finance.appledaily.com/realtime/20190330/1542505/?itm_source=twad_web&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_campaign=twad_marquee&amp;itm_content=marquee</a>"},{"pid":"fa811cba9dd148b227e4aac90d110c96268e1884","tid":1084302,"uid":1130,"like":25,"dislike":4,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"A7真係神U嚟"},{"pid":"f2519739218fe7be6bc1a51db2143f3e70fa277b","tid":1084302,"uid":220734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa811cba9dd148b227e4aac90d110c96268e1884","tid":1084302,"uid":1130,"like":25,"dislike":4,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"A7真係神U嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:01:40.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"302dc2b99d7b7eb44b228b7f836b1ed329b54202","tid":1084302,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa811cba9dd148b227e4aac90d110c96268e1884","tid":1084302,"uid":1130,"like":25,"dislike":4,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"A7真係神U嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:04:22.000Z","msg":"Why"},{"pid":"10858c0e8c5187f023b8870354f65ff54cac504c","tid":1084302,"uid":231725,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"fa811cba9dd148b227e4aac90d110c96268e1884","tid":1084302,"uid":1130,"like":25,"dislike":4,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"A7真係神U嚟"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"Apple 第一粒64bit soc<br />\n快過A6一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eeec385a3d41de4c55493192005613c61b97aa4","tid":1084302,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:26:14.000Z","msg":"過檔華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff40a62a0d6fd5f2d777796284be3181e52ea77d","tid":1084302,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:29:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e024b05ca6958f07c3687223897956649e3fc00d","tid":1084302,"uid":1130,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"10858c0e8c5187f023b8870354f65ff54cac504c","tid":1084302,"uid":231725,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"fa811cba9dd148b2